title: Lilja 4 Real
description:
With people being thrown into poverty with the fall of the Soviet Union, trafficking has become a serious problem in Eastern Europe.
Trying to find the relatives of one of the victims, Dangoule, who was the girl in the film &#039;Lilja 4 Ever&#039;, Swedish television uncovers some of the trafficking networks in Europe.
